        <heading>1065.  Reconventional demand exceeding principal demand</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 1065.  Reconventional demand exceeding principal demand
The reconventional demand may or may not diminish or defeat the recovery sought in the principal demand.  It may claim relief exceeding in amount that sought in the principal demand.</p>
        </content>
